  &lt;/video&gt;
  
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;When I saw the logo, I immediately thought of gyroscopic rings that eventually locked into place. The client also wanted the rings to lock into place at the end like lens elements (as cameras are an integral part of their workflow). The back plate is also a custom dark onyx material that strengthens the feeling of quality and solidarity.&lt;/p&gt;

